# FORMAT: Surge Ruleset
# SOURCES: Official service sites, SukkaW/Surge, Rabbit-Spec/Surge, blackmatrix7/ios_rule_script, QuixoticHeart/rule-set
# NOTE: International AI services, including Apple Intelligence, assistants, model platforms, coding agents, research, productivity and generative media.
# NOTE: Mainland China AI products, generic analytics and identity providers, shared cloud ranges and unverified single-host IP rules are intentionally excluded.
# NOTE: Product-root domains are included where the AI application cannot be separated from the vendor website by hostname.

